![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-13T20-12-00-03-00/630_360_1686647350-2935.jpeg)

[ ![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-13T20-12-00-03-00/630_360_1686647350-2935.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686647350-2935.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-13T20-12-00-03-00/630_360_1686647350-1161.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686647350-1161.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-13T20-12-00-03-00/630_360_1686647350-7684.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686647350-7684.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-13T20-12-00-03-00/630_360_1686647350-6675.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686647350-6675.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-13T20-12-00-03-00/630_360_1686647350-3410.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686647350-3410.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-06-13T20-12-00-03-00/630_360_1686647350-7474.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_06/1686647350-7474.jpeg)

